<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī </hi>Ituvummoru paḻaṅkalpaṭi <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> kom<unclear>āṟa</unclear>ṉcaṭaiyaṟkku yāṇṭu nāṉkāvatu peraiyūrnāṭṭu [[paṉaiyūr Araiyaṉ kaḷva]]44 ṉ tirukkoṭikāvil <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>vaṟkku nontāviḷakkiṉukku kuṭu<unclear>t</unclear>ta cempoṉ patiṉaiṅ <unclear>ka</unclear>ḻañcu <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> I
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>ta</unclear>ṉ palicaiyāl nālu Uḻakkum piḻaiy<unclear>ān</unclear>āḻikkiḻ Uḻakkiṉnāl nicati Uḻakku neyyu [[mittaḷikke kuṇaṉtu A]]ccippārkkaḷantu kuṭuppo<unclear>mā</unclear>y Ippoṉ koṇṭom nāraṇakka caturvetimaṅkalattu<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> 
<lb n="3"/>Itu paḻayakalpaṭi Inta<hi rend="grantha">srī</hi>vimānattile Eṟa veṭṭinamaiyil muṉṉivā <hi rend="grantha">jaga</hi>m veṭṭikkiṭanta taṉikkallāl U<hi rend="grantha">bhai</hi>yokam Illāmaiyāl Atu taviṉtatu <supplied reason="omitted">|</supplied> Itu muṭṭil paṉmāy[[e]]<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>re kaṭaikkuṭṭapeṟṟār <supplied reason="omitted">||</supplied>
</p>

</div>

